						               													<description>A twist on the family classic monster chases around the house, evolving it into a new format of flip and chase.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;One player is the monsterous game-master Pooman, flipping the cards selected by the other players to reveal an array of characters.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Cards flipped reveal either collectable character cards, special cards or Pooman cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Character cards have puntastic names like 'Uriah Niles', and can have brown stars for players to bank points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Special Cards can have powers to help defend against the Pooman, like freezing power of the 'Poocicle'.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If a Pooman is revealed then players must RUN the game-master will count to 10 and chase the player with the most stars; &amp;#10;if any player is grabbed by the Pooman then all their cards are lost! First player to collect 5 brown stars wins!&amp;#10;Each pack includes 10 blank cards for players to create their own characters.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A new twist on an old classic - varying it so the chase is in short bursts and players can apply tactics and compete against other players to win victory over the Pooman.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
